p: In addition, PubChem ID: 135413534 also has activity on all the three sites. The number of HB interactions on Site 1, Site 2 and Site 3 are 5, 4 and 6, respectively. The HB interactive amino acid with Site 1, Site 2 and Site 3 corresponds to five amino acid (ARG107 in Chain A and ASN75 (2), ASN153, HIE145 in Chain B), four AA (ASN75, ASN77 in Chain A and ALA173, ARG92 in Chain B) and six AA (ALA55 in Chain C and ASN75 (2), ASN154(2), ASN77), respectively.
